#############

# app
11 3 * * 2-6 app-scale app-east 20
12 3 * * 2-6 app-scale app-west 20

# apptest
14 3 * * 2-6 app-scale app-test-1 5
15 3 * * 2-6 app-scale app-test-2 5

# crowdsourcing
16 3 * * 2-6 app-scale cs 10

