# scale up
###########

# app
4 10 * * 1-5 app-scale app-east 40
5 10 * * 1-5 app-scale app-west 40

# apptest
7 10 * * 1-5 app-scale app-test-1 10
8 10 * * 1-5 app-scale app-test-2 10

# crowdsourcing
9 10 * * 1-5 app-scale cs 30
